# Tooling configs

## Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `biome.json` | Biome formatting + linting rules |
| `tsconfig.json` | Root TypeScript config (all packages share) |
| `vitest.config.ts` | Test runner config (coverage, bundle-phobia, thresholds) |
| `pnpm-workspace.yaml` | pnpm workspace definition |
| `.changeset/config.json` | Changesets versioning config |
| `mcp.json` | MCP server configuration (Linear, Codegraph, etc.) |
| `.gitignore` | Global ignore patterns |
| `package.json` | Root scripts + private workspace |

## Per-package files

| File | Required | Notes |
|------|----------|-------|
| `package.json` | Yes | Version `0.0.0`, build/test scripts, peer deps |
| `README.md` | Yes | npm readme, English only |
| `CHANGELOG.md` | Yes | Maintained by Changesets |
| `tsconfig.json` | No | Only if package-specific overrides needed |
| `biome.json` | No | Only if package-specific overrides needed |

## Demo app files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `apps/demo/astro.config.ts` | Astro + Starlight config with Vite aliases |
| `apps/demo/package.json` | Demo dependencies (`workspace:*` refs) |
| `apps/demo/tsconfig.json` | `paths` entries for all packages |
| `apps/demo/src/entrypoint.ts` | Alpine plugin registrations |
| `apps/demo/src/plugin-nav.ts` | Sidebar navigation |
| `apps/demo/src/demo/playground-demos.ts` | Demo component registry |

## CI files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `.github/workflows/ci.yml` | Test + lint + typecheck on PRs |
| `.github/workflows/release.yml` | Publish to npm on merge to master |
| `.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/*.yml` | Bug report + feature request templates |

## Terminal tooling

- If `rtk` is installed and command is supported, prefer `rtk` for terminal workflows to reduce noisy output and token usage.
- Applies to shell commands such as `git`, `gh`, `pnpm`, test runners, search commands, and log inspection.
- Does not replace built-in structured tools like `Read`, `Grep`, or `Glob`; use `rtk` only for terminal/Bash flows.

## Common mistakes

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Edit `vitest.config.ts` without checking thresholds | Check `pnpm run test:coverage` passes |
| Add new package without updating `apps/demo/package.json` | Add `workspace:*` dep |
| Add new package without updating `apps/demo/tsconfig.json` | Add `paths` entry |
| Forget `.changeset/*.md` before merge | Run `pnpm run changeset` |
